00:04:41.133 --> 00:04:42.133
- THAT'D BE GREAT.

00:04:42.133 --> 00:04:45.066
[cheers and applause]

00:04:45.066 --> 00:04:46.633
- ALL RIGHT.

00:04:46.633 --> 00:04:48.400
MAYBE YOU SHOULD COME BACK
WITH HIM TOO.

00:04:48.400 --> 00:04:49.466
- OH, WELL, YEAH, SURE.

00:04:49.466 --> 00:04:50.900
- SO, YEAH,
Y'ALL SHOULD COME BACK,

00:04:50.900 --> 00:04:53.533
SO WE'LL SEE Y'ALL BACK HERE
